Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:06.03,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:09.21,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:15.62,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,秋子阿姨怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:19.41,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,名雪做了什锦菜粥 正在喂她吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.65,0:00:20.52,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:28.96,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,你怎么了 好像脸色不太好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:32.66,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,啊 大概因为外面有点冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:38.25,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,栞是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:40.71,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,我对她说了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:43.00,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,因为她说无论如何都想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:45.00,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,所以我告诉她了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:50.31,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,真的没弄错吗 那个 到这次的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:52.17,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,医生是那么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:56.23,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,即使能活到生日 接下来也不久了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:00:59.40,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,我没告诉名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:01.18,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,因为不想让她担心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:06.46,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,但是因为相泽君最近和栞关系很好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.53,0:01:08.64,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,所以我想要和你说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:11.36,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,嗯 多谢你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:16.89,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,再见了 我的家是往这边的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:18.66,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,等一下啊 香里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.59,0:01:23.87,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,栞的生日是下周日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.59,0:01:27.67,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,这样好吗 那样地无视栞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.03,0:01:29.48,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,已经没多少时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:33.01,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,那孩子和你在一起的时候也在笑着？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:37.64,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,是啊 没看到过她哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:38.88,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:43.63,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,喂 香里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:52.54,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,祐一君 偶要进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:57.47,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,哇 一片漆黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:01:59.66,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,可以开灯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:01.57,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,不 不要开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:02.96,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:05.71,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,一旦见到光亮我就会变成灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:10.24,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,祐一君是吸血鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:12.07,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,找我有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:14.00,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,不 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:18.27,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,只是不知为什么觉得呆在你的身边比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:20.54,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:21.70,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:24.75,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,你真是奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:25.78,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:29.73,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:09.40,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,躁狂既止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:12.80,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,然失其心智
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:16.50,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,行卧之态一如稚儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:19.57,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,询以医者观之 曰 神劳心惑者甚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:22.92,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,是与『妄想』之症也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:28.45,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,今天姐姐和妹妹都请假吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:36.20,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,如果是掉了东西 能一起找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:40.31,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,如果是以魔物为对手 能一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.16,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,但栞是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.70,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,我说 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.20,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,你当时是怎样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:55.75,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,你觉得我应该为仅剩少许时间的女孩做点什么才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:20.45,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,这里是晚上比较美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:24.00,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,我怕冷 所以觉得白天的好
